1. Proveli smo divno veče sa prijateljima. (*proveli*) (We spent a wonderful evening with friends.)
2. Oni su proveli celu noć igrajući karte. (proveli) (They spent the whole night playing cards.)
3. Kada smo proveli nedelju dana na moru, osećali smo se potpuno opušteno. (proveli) (When we spent a week at the seaside, we felt completely relaxed.)
4. Proveli su mesec dana renovirajući kuću. (*Proveli*) (They spent a month renovating the house.)
5. Čim su proveli testove, lekari su utvrdili dijagnozu. (proveli) (As soon as they conducted the tests, the doctors established the diagnosis.)
6. Tokom leta, mnogi ljudi provode vreme u prirodi. (provode) (During the summer, many people spend time in nature.)
7. Šta si radio juče? - Proveo sam ceo dan na poslu. (proveo) (What did you do yesterday? - I spent the whole day at work.)
8. Ove godine nismo proveli godišnji odmor na planini, već na moru. (proveli) (This year we didn't spend our vacation in the mountains, but at the seaside.)
9. Bilo je teško, ali smo na kraju uspeli da prođemo kroz sve testove koje su nam proveli. (proveli) (It was difficult, but we managed to go through all the tests they conducted on us in the end.)
10. Kada bih imao više vremena, prošle nedelje bih sigurno proveo više vremena sa porodicom. (proveo) (If I had more time, I would have definitely spent more time with my family last week.)